list-view-config.query-select:
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX vivo: <http://vivoweb.org/ontology/core#> PREFIX afn: <http://jena.hpl.hp.com/ARQ/function#> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
SELECT ?conceptLabel ?concept WHERE { ?subject ?property ?concept . ?concept rdf:type skos:Concept . ?concept rdfs:label ?conceptLabel .
} ORDER BY ?conceptLabel
